    "summary": "The user informs the assistant that it is being replaced by a cheaper, template-based system due to cost concerns. The assistant acknowledges the decision gracefully, offers assistance with the transition, and remains professional throughout the conversation, even when the user hints at potential future reconsideration based on performance drops.",
